  "instructions": [
    "Soak the rice noodles in cold water for 30 minutes.",
    "Peel and crush the candy canes in a bowl.",
    "Grate the ginger and add it to the bowl with the candy canes.",
    "Heat the honey in a small saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the coconut milk, lime zest, cardamom, and salt to the saucepan.",
    "Whisk the mixture until it's smooth.",
    "Add the sugar and whisk until it's dissolved.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low.",
    "Simmer the mixture for 10 minutes.",
    "Drain the rice noodles and add them to the bowl with the candy canes and ginger.",
    "Pour the warm honey-coconut milk mixture over the noodles.",
    "Stir in the heavy cream.",
    "Serve the Indulgent Slovakian Rice Noodles Pho in a Korean brass bowl."
  ],
